    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A normal school with a strange rule... </h2>Due to a certain situation, you are the new member of the Detective Club. Alongside the scatterbrained Alice Baskerville, you'll have to solve your first case as a detective! <strong>The future of the club is in your hands!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024690/extras/e452d59510d457757fb6bb07147f7077.avif?t=1748809268\" width=342 height=105 /></span><br><br>Using logical deduction, you'll be able to <strong>connect the evidence</strong> to formulate hypotheses about what really happened. <strong>Ask the right questions</strong> to identify <strong>inconsistencies in the testimonies</strong> and <strong>solve puzzles</strong> that challenge <i>your deductive reasoning!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short and charismatic comedy story, 2 hours of gameplay.<br></li><li>Puzzle mini-games.<br></li><li>Make interrogations, ask the right questions and find the inconsistencies in the testimonies.<br></li><li>A notepad where you will be able to see all the collected evidences.<br></li><li>A debate with everyone involved, choose your best argument to affirm or deny the accusations.<br></li><li>A story with many references to Sherlock Holmes!</li></ul>",
